=======
Changes
=======

0.3.0
=======

 - Term.codes values are saved as string (not bytes in python3)
 - rename `pyterm._` to `pyterm.decode`
 - add method `Pyterm.format` like `string.format`

0.2.0 (2013-10-14)
=====================

 - added option to force the use of ANSI codes
 - if curses not available fall back to use of ANSI codes
 - Term.lines() and Term.cols() use 'stty' when not using curses

0.1.0 (2013-10-11)
======================

 - Initial release
